00:39:31.040 --> 00:39:32.670
&gt;&gt; Ellen Cassedy: So the question
is whether there were any outside

00:39:32.670 --> 00:39:37.120
influences on this writer, outside
the Yiddish literary circle.

00:39:37.120 --> 00:39:39.740
&gt;&gt; Yermiyahu Ahron Talb: Go ahead.

00:39:39.740 --> 00:39:42.160
&gt;&gt; Ellen Cassedy: She always
said that she wasn't influenced

00:39:42.160 --> 00:39:45.960
by anybody, that she was not
part of any literary school,

00:39:45.960 --> 00:39:49.980
and that she pursued her
own path and didn't borrow

00:39:49.980 --> 00:39:52.640
