00:40:44.050 --> 00:40:48.180
Grace Paley, and Gabrielle
Garcia-Marquez,

00:40:48.180 --> 00:40:52.140
surreal butterflies,
sunbeams, and so on.

00:40:52.140 --> 00:40:53.550
So you could sort of see that.

00:40:53.550 --> 00:40:56.790
But I don't think she read
either of those writers.

00:40:56.790 --> 00:41:00.930
